lass="article-author-bio__body"><p>Kevin Baker is a contributing editor at <i>The New Republic</i> and the author of <i><a href="http://www.workman.com/products/9781579657291/">America the Ingenious</a>. </i>He is finishing a history of New York City baseball.</p></div></div></div><div class="footer-wrap newsletter-cta"></div><div class="footer-wrap footer-text-wrap"><div class="footer-tags"><span class="footer-tags__title">Read More: </span><div class="tag-list"><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-feature " href="/tags/feature">Feature</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-magazine " href="/tags/magazine">Magazine</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-april-2017 " href="/tags/april-2017">April 2017</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-politics " href="/tags/politics">Politics</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-secession " href="/tags/secession">Secession</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-blue-state " href="/tags/blue-state">Blue State</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-red-state " href="/tags/red-state">Red State</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-election-2016 " href="/tags/election-2016">Election 2016</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-labor " href="/tags/labor">Labor</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-michigan " href="/tags/michigan">Michigan</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-wisconsin " href="/tags/wisconsin">Wisconsin</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class=