an class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-hawaii " href="/tags/hawaii">Hawaii</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-colorado " href="/tags/colorado">Colorado</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-new-mexico " href="/tags/new-mexico">New Mexico</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-kansas " href="/tags/kansas">Kansas</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-nebraska " href="/tags/nebraska">Nebraska</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-idaho " href="/tags/idaho">Idaho</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-minnesota " href="/tags/minnesota">Minnesota</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-illinois " href="/tags/illinois">Illinois</a><span class="tag-list-comma">, </span></span><span class="tag-list-item"><a class="tag tag-culture " href="/tags/culture">Culture</a><span class="tag-list-comma"></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></article></main><div class="ContainerPlacement OutBrain Engage-Wrapper"><div class="ContainerSection OutBrain Engage"><div class="OB-REACT-WRAPPER"><div class="OUTBRAIN" data-src="https://newrepublic.com/article/140948/bluexit-blue-states-exit-trump-red-america"></div></div></div></div><div class="ad-unit ad-house_donate "><div class="htlad-House_DONATE"></div></div><footer class="footer fade-in " id="footer"><div class="footer__topRow"><ul class="footer__verticalsNav"><li><a href="/feeds/168326/breaking-news">BREAKING NEWS</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/politics">POLITICS</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52"